5","title":"India's capital goods sector shows steady recovery, driven by genset demand from data centers, manufacturing, airports, and hospitals. Cummins India and Kirloskar Oil Engines lead.\nCummins sees 18% CAGR FY25-28 with strong power gen demand, BESS potential. Kirloskar reports strong growth in power gen, defense projects, and MENA exports, projecting 15-18% CAGR FY25-28.","summary":"India's capital goods sector shows steady recovery, driven by genset demand from data centers, manufacturing, airports, and hospitals. Cummins India and Kirloskar Oil Engines lead.\nCummins sees 18% CAGR FY25-28 with strong power gen demand, BESS potential. Kirloskar reports strong growth in power gen, defense projects, and MENA exports, projecting 15-18% CAGR FY25-28.","url":"https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/markets/stocks/news/capital-goods-recovery-underway-focus-on-cummins-india-and-kirloskar-oil-engines/articleshow/124657778.cms","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-10-18T00:00:00","source":"The Economic Times"},{"id":"315426","title":"Kirloskar Group aims to double revenue to ₹5 billion by 2030.\nPlans ₹5,000 cr investment across Kirloskar Oil, Pneumatic, Ferrous, Industries.","summary":"Kirloskar Group aims to double revenue to ₹5 billion by 2030.\nPlans ₹5,000 cr investment across Kirloskar Oil, Pneumatic, Ferrous, Industries.","url":"https://www.livemint.com/companies/kirloskar-group-2-billion-revenue-by-fy30-lines-up-5-000-crore-investment-11760266392456.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2025-10-13T06:00:08","source":"Livemint"}]}]